text: Sport União Sintrense is a Portuguese football club based in Sintra, that plays in the Campeonato de Portugal, the third division of Portuguese football. The club was established on 7 October 1911. ==Current squad== ==Notable former players== * Nelson Semedo ==References== ==External links== Category:Football clubs in Portugal Category:Football clubs in Lisbon Category:Association football clubs established in 1911 Category:1911 establishments in Portugal
